Package com.path.android.jobqueue

Interface Summary
JobManager.QueueFactory Interface to supply custom JobQueues for JobManager
JobQueue Interface that any JobQueue should implement These job queues can be given to JobManager.
 

Class Summary
BaseJob  
JobHolder Container class to address Jobs inside job manager.
JobManager a JobManager that supports; -> Persistent / Non Persistent Jobs -> Job Priority -> Running Jobs in Parallel -> Stats like waiting Job Count
JobManager.DefaultQueueFactory Default implementation of QueueFactory that creates one SqliteJobQueue and one NonPersistentPriorityQueue
